# zathura — wildcharm-themed document viewer (PDF/EPUB/DjVu/CBZ). Behaviour and
# future non-colour settings live here (direct-edit); ALL colours (+ the recolor
# block) live in the GENERATED theme-{dark,light} pair (themes/hestia/render.py
# — edit palette.yml + re-render), symlinked by the bootstrap as `theme` per
# `theme_variant`. zathura resolves the include relative to this config's dir.
# Recolour (dark-mode page inversion) is on by default on the dark desktop, off on
# light; toggle per-document with `r`.

include theme
